"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec66ca18e983ec8aa352df7c0750a4ddd6904be8","tid":723363,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42f07fd89d34449c07890f96324758bec536c103","tid":723363,"uid":19527,"like":52,"dislike":0,"score":52,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T10:34:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/30/183412_11c7ddaa836fe74dbbf1424aba3fe161.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F30%2F183412_11c7ddaa836fe74dbbf1424aba3fe161.png&h=b300b0f5&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T11:25:23.000Z","msg":"哩個伯死咗未？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T12:32:55.000Z","msg":"先知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d0fc7571e2d4386ae074cbd56e62e709ea53ec7","tid":723363,"uid":52595,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T12:42:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e76273f4622dc525a98abe7315fcf5735bd44905","tid":723363,"uid":124107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T12:52:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"52d64422e7814e3b6c13b733972aaf0549681913","tid":723363,"uid":69924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eacec5f8f1a5ed633f45bc1c0215ba4d902ee53d","tid":723363,"uid":86508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T11:00:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>天水圍街市買野貴就人所共知，但其實小商戶都係比街市焗撚住。<br />\n<br />\n領展租貴就唔再講，好多街市既洗費直接向租戶收返，例如街市搞既會員計劃。c9買餸可以啪卡儲分換禮物，好似好抵屌，其實每一分都要同租戶收返，租戶無得選擇參唔參與會員計劃，因為街市強迫租戶簽租時簽署連帶條款，唔簽就唔租。<br />\n<br />\n同時間，街市每月向所有租戶收取所謂宣傳費，但只搞門面工作，並未有為不同租戶宣傳。有時候搞時段特價活動亦係強迫租戶比折扣，例如咩火鍋節 焗海鮮檔搞幾蚊買海鮮活；又係平時焗生果檔比折，試諗下比街市搞一搞點可以唔貴<br />\n<br />\n當然你可以話「咁你唔好租咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」但係街市自己有一班人係到玩，有5-10%鋪位自己人租左，方便控制住價格。<span style=\"color: red;\">如果有普通租戶退出唔玩，佢地就會放自己友落黎，所以你基本上買唔到平野。<br />\n</span><br />\n好多租戶都唔想簽呢D連帶條款，有冇大神知道租戶可唔可以反對到？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n聽識得魚檔講, 係新開街市租比一般租戶, 等你幫佢儲到一班客, 之後唔租比你<br />\n<br />\n佢而家情況係官方自己友佢對面已經開左檔同佢打對台, 但佢來貨平, 所以平賣益街坊, 點知而家到期話唔租比佢 (自願+$8000 都唔租比佢)"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T06:00:02.000Z","msg":"商業世界係咁 你估仲係房署ar<br />\n<br />\n房署管果時大家日日話佢管得差  而家領展管得好左啦但唔侵你玩"},{"pid":"f7562df77559a62f91b4c44083b90fe65db63c8a","tid":723363,"uid":69924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1af61ee337b3a1bc34fd398817fb4eca4e696435","tid":723363,"uid":174611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d15cc62ce48e6fd27f8b7a71dd2c494307d0f021","tid":723363,"uid":15018,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"182628c37b8274c1a7b041df5f36946d45cc435a","tid":723363,"uid":157841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T11:26:56.000Z","msg":"傾唔啱咪唔做 如果條款太苛刻業主都要承擔租唔出嘅風險"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T11:35:22.000Z","msg":"終於有人講道理 其實自由主場根本就係咁 on9 講到班租戶水深火熱 賺唔到錢你估佢地仲租唔租<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T11:44:26.000Z","msg":"你都on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果市場對你份工underpaid你可唔可以唔做？<br />\n當然你可以話你一定會唔撚做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係好撚多人無得揀<br />\nUnderpaid都係有錢賺 你係唔係唔出聲成世照做？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T06:03:24.000Z","msg":"何謂underpaid？"},{"pid":"2d83e8e7fc19f0c4d0b681e456c1ec3e89bca8d0","tid":723363,"uid":156547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c9aefcf8375ce700c1a0c169ad7bf037c065fe4","tid":723363,"uid":174611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec66ca18e983ec8aa352df7c0750a4ddd6904be8","tid":723363,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42f07fd89d34449c07890f96324758bec536c103","tid":723363,"uid":19527,"like":52,"dislike":0,"score":52,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-30